quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  79,1,Mede (Soro abͻfoͻ a wͻ’yi abͻneεfoͻ no nkwa wͻ) ahometeε soͻ
  79,2,Ne (Soro abͻfoͻ a wͻ’yi apapafoͻ no nkwa) wͻ anigyeε ne ahosεpε soͻ
  79,3,"Ne (Soro abͻfoͻ a), wͻ’dware sε asudwarefoͻ de Nyankopͻn ahyεdeε no ba"
  79,4,Na wͻ’yε ntεntεm sε akansifoͻ
  79,5,Na wͻ’toto Nyankopͻn Ahyεdeε no di nse sε
  79,6,Ɛda a awosoͻ no bεwoso deε edikan
  79,7,Na deε εtͻso mmienu no bεtoa soͻ no
  79,8,"Saa Da no, akoma bεbͻ binim (ama onipa ho awoso)"
  79,9,Ebinom ani bewu
  79,10,"Wͻ’ka sε: “Enti yε’bεsan anyane aba nkwa tebea mu bio"
  79,11,"Aberε a (y’awu) ayε nnompe a, ahunu?”"
  79,12,"Wͻ’ka sε: “Sε (Wusͻreε no yε nokorε ampa a), εneε na yεresan aba nkwa mu bio no bεyε brεguo (ama yεn Kaafirfoͻ no)“"
  79,13,(Owusͻreε no) yε Nteamu baako pε
  79,14,"Na deε wͻ’behunu ara nesε, wͻ’anyane afri owuo mu na wͻn wͻ asaase soͻ"
  79,15,Enti Mose ho asεm no abeduru wo hͻ
  79,16,Ɛberε a ne Wura Nyankopͻn frεε no wͻ Bonhwa kronkron Tuwa mu hͻ no
  79,17,"Ɔka kyerεε no sε: “Kͻ Farao hͻ, na nokorε sε wate atua, ayε bͻne atra so “"
  79,18,"Na ka kyerε no sε: “Wopε sε woyε kronkron"
  79,19,Na menkyerε wo kwan nkͻ wo Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ na nya Neho suro?”
  79,20,Ɔde Nsεnkyerεnee akεseε no kyerεε no
  79,21,"Nanso ᴐfaa no atorᴐsԑm, yεε asoͻden nso"
  79,22,"Afei ͻdanee n’akyi maae, bͻͻ mmͻden (sε ͻbεko atia Mose ne ne Nyankopͻn)"
  79,23,Ɔboaboaa nenkorͻfoͻ ano paee mu (detoo wͻn anim)
  79,24,"Ɔkaa sε: “Me ne mo wura kokuroko no “"
  79,25,Enti Nyankopͻn de daakye ne seseei (wiase) asotwee no twee n’aso
  79,26,"Nokorε sε, adesua wͻ woi mu dema obi a osuro Nyankopͻn"